{{italictitle}}
'''''Evan Almighty''''' is a 2007 [[United States|American]] comedy movie and a spin-off sequel to ''[[Bruce Almighty]]''. It stars [[Steve Carell]], [[Morgan Freeman]], [[Molly Shannon]], [[John Goodman]], [[Wanda Sykes]], and [[Jonah Hill]]. 

It is about congressman, Evan Baxter, trying to save many animals before a massive flood wipes-out an entire forest after he was sent by [[God]]. It was released on June 22, 2007 to negative reviews.

